    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your rowing team and lead it to victory. You will have to find your own sources of income, provide the team with everything they need. Manage their training, as well as constantly make sure that they do not get into trouble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your way will stand competitors, authorities, organizers of underground races and a lot of those who believe that the only way to success in sports is money. Will you be able to prove otherwise?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Your task: to get the gold of the Olympics and prove to everyone that hard work wins in sports!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d074b9eb661c81786380f3b64ab0cf11.poster.avif?t=1766578044\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d074b9eb661c81786380f3b64ab0cf11.webm?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d074b9eb661c81786380f3b64ab0cf11.mp4?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Many decisions will separate you from the goal, and each will not be simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/79377a327f9165ed588e46700b9579f1.poster.avif?t=1766578044\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/79377a327f9165ed588e46700b9579f1.webm?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/79377a327f9165ed588e46700b9579f1.mp4?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Participate in races, take prizes and improve your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/6d469f425937ef60f3b51e6e9a3896dd.poster.avif?t=1766578044\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/6d469f425937ef60f3b51e6e9a3896dd.webm?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/6d469f425937ef60f3b51e6e9a3896dd.mp4?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fair way or bypass maneuvers? You decide how to get to the finals and what you are willing to sacrifice for the cherished goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d07787384d7f37538b761d3bb7d24265.poster.avif?t=1766578044\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d07787384d7f37538b761d3bb7d24265.webm?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320490/extras/d07787384d7f37538b761d3bb7d24265.mp4?t=1766578044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
